{"tid":1364911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔好請求外軍入元朗掃黑？","createTime":"2019-07-25T13:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T14:18:47.000Z","uid":201464,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5416f388b322cd3bbe5983f46341f842d9962916","tid":1364911,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:01:38.000Z","msg":"香港政府已經被架空，警黑已融為一體（兩個都係under鄧xx），有咗請求解放軍/美軍/un維和部隊入元朗掃黑嘅諗法：<br />\n解放軍：最快嚟到，但係到時好大機會掃埋我哋，直接軍管<br />\n美軍：都幾快嚟到，但係到時會俾人話入侵中國領土，到時都幾大獲<br />\nun維和部隊：算係最好，始終中國係un成員之一，大家都有份，不過最耐先嚟到，同埋最難有機會出（始終香港唔係第三世界）"},{"pid":"cc51040948832943c6c7cba070ccc9ad62acc331","tid":1364911,"uid":33477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"第三個係冇撚用架喎"},{"pid":"10287aa0f6814b2c1fcdaa9c22db67728abe6d52","tid":1364911,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa49647ca4baa87a39dcd0ff461b71d517ee057","tid":1364911,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc51040948832943c6c7cba070ccc9ad62acc331","tid":1364911,"uid":33477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"第三個係冇撚用架喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"點解咁講"},{"pid":"b4d75da3c55194e623f4d5dea9ec7d28764cb32b","tid":1364911,"uid":25569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:05:21.000Z","msg":"邊個得閒干涉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3232ea432afc19f8d2bb02ae00866a4dd0e721f1","tid":1364911,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個得閒干涉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家全世界睇住"},{"pid":"1dc05250802